<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<puzzle>
<help>
  <![CDATA[
1. Your goal is to write a number in every blank tile (without a diagonal line).
2. The number on the top of a column or at the left of a row, gives you the sum of the numbers in that column or row.
3. You can write numbers 1 to 9 in the tiles, however no same number should appear in a consecutive row or column.
4. Tiles which only have a diagonal line aren't used in the game.
  ]]>
</help>
